posting_body: ['Spacious OLD TOWN 1.5 beds w/ AC!~ Private balcony..Must SEE!', 'Pets OK', 'Listing ID #: 1695', 'Address: 1220 N LaSalle, #1220-G5', 'Price: $2,495', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.5', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Approx.', 'Size: 1 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Floor: 5', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Building Amenities', 'Garage', 'Laundry', 'Storage', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Balcony', 'Dishwasher', 'Eat In Kitchen', 'Hardwood', 'Old Town 1.5 beds with Central Air and a private balcony is located just steps away from the Clark/Division Red Line.', 'You are able to explore Lincoln Park, Lakeview, Loop, Andersonville, Ravenswood and more.', 'Spend a relaxing afternoon at Lincoln Park zoo or at Oak Street beach.', 'Prime location with a brand new Jewel, tons of restuarants, shops, gyms and more.', "The location is one that can't be beat!", 'This one-of-a-kind 1.5 beds apartment has an updated kitchen with a dishwasher, a spacious floorplan, hardwood floors, walk in closet and a private balcony with sliding door.', "Central air and heat, Laundry in building, parking(for an extra monthly fee), elevator and on site maintenance makes this apartment one you can't pass up!", 'Josh S', 'Phone: (312) 313-6927', 'Beal Properties \xa0 (312) 313-6927 \xa0 josh.', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Josh S at (312) 313-6927', '243']
